- Architecture & modules: [ARCHITECTURE.md](mdc:ARCHITECTURE.md)
- Build & deployment: [DEPLOYMENT.md](mdc:DEPLOYMENT.md)

## Coding Conventions

- Indentation: 4 spaces, no tabs
- All output files in English (code, comments, docs)
- README.md always present in project root
- Follow standard Go project structure (cmd/, internal/)
- Secrets only via env vars, never in code
- New AI providers via `ai.Provider` interface and `Respond(ctx, ai.Request)`
- Thread-safe access to shared state via mutex
